---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import PageHeader from '../components/PageHeader.astro';
import CTA from '../components/CTA.astro';
import { Check, Phone, Settings, Calendar, Shield, AlertTriangle } from 'lucide-astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Stairlift Servicing & Maintenance | Sheffield & South Yorkshire"
  description="Professional stairlift servicing in South Yorkshire. Keep your stairlift running safely with regular maintenance. Call 0114 2347195 to book a service."
>
  <PageHeader
    title="Service & Maintenance"
    subtitle="Keep your stairlift running safely and smoothly"
  />

  <section class="py-16 lg:py-20">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-12">
        <!-- Main content -->
        <div class="lg:col-span-2">
          <p class="text-lg text-slate-600 mb-8">
            Regular servicing is essential to keep your stairlift operating safely and reliably.
            Like any mechanical equipment, stairlifts need routine maintenance to ensure they
            continue to work when you need them most.
          </p>

          <div class="bg-primary-50 border border-primary-100 rounded-xl p-6 mb-10">
            <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
              <Calendar class="w-6 h-6 text-primary-600 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" />
              <div>
                <h3 class="font-semibold text-primary-800 mb-2">How Often Should You Service?</h3>
                <p class="text-primary-700">
                  We recommend servicing your stairlift at least once a year to maintain optimal
                  performance and safety. More frequent servicing may be needed for heavily used lifts.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-6">What's Included in a Service?</h2>

          <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4 mb-10">
            <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <Check class="w-5 h-5 text-green-500 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" />
              <span class="text-slate-700">Full safety inspection</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <Check class="w-5 h-5 text-green-500 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" />
              <span class="text-slate-700">Battery check and testing</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <Check class="w-5 h-5 text-green-500 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" />
              <span class="text-slate-700">Track cleaning and lubrication</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <Check class="w-5 h-5 text-green-500 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" />
              <span class="text-slate-700">Motor and gearbox inspection</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <Check class="w-5 h-5 text-green-500 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" />
              <span class="text-slate-700">Seat swivel mechanism check</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <Check class="w-5 h-5 text-green-500 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" />
              <span class="text-slate-700">Safety sensor testing</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <Check class="w-5 h-5 text-green-500 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" />
              <span class="text-slate-700">Remote control check</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <Check class="w-5 h-5 text-green-500 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" />
              <span class="text-slate-700">Electrical connections check</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <Check class="w-5 h-5 text-green-500 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" />
              <span class="text-slate-700">Belt and drive inspection</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <Check class="w-5 h-5 text-green-500 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" />
              <span class="text-slate-700">Footrest and armrest adjustment</span>
            </div>
          </div>

          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-6">Benefits of Regular Servicing</h2>

          <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 mb-10">
            <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 border border-slate-100 shadow-sm">
              <Shield class="w-8 h-8 text-primary-600 mb-4" />
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-2">Safety Assurance</h3>
              <p class="text-sm text-slate-600">
                Ensure all safety features are working correctly to protect you and your family.
              </p>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 border border-slate-100 shadow-sm">
              <Settings class="w-8 h-8 text-primary-600 mb-4" />
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-2">Prevent Breakdowns</h3>
              <p class="text-sm text-slate-600">
                Catch potential problems early before they become expensive repairs.
              </p>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 border border-slate-100 shadow-sm">
              <Calendar class="w-8 h-8 text-primary-600 mb-4" />
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-2">Extended Lifespan</h3>
              <p class="text-sm text-slate-600">
                Regular maintenance helps your stairlift last longer and run more efficiently.
              </p>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 border border-slate-100 shadow-sm">
              <Check class="w-8 h-8 text-primary-600 mb-4" />
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-2">Peace of Mind</h3>
              <p class="text-sm text-slate-600">
                Know your stairlift is in top condition and ready when you need it.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-amber-50 border border-amber-200 rounded-xl p-6">
            <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
              <AlertTriangle class="w-6 h-6 text-amber-600 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" />
              <div>
                <h3 class="font-semibold text-amber-800 mb-2">Signs Your Stairlift Needs Attention</h3>
                <ul class="space-y-2 text-amber-700">
                  <li>• Unusual noises during operation</li>
                  <li>• Slower than normal movement</li>
                  <li>• Jerky or uneven travel</li>
                  <li>• Warning lights or beeping</li>
                  <li>• Battery not holding charge</li>
                </ul>
                <p class="mt-4 text-amber-700">
                  If you notice any of these signs, call us on{' '}
                  <a href="tel:01142347195" class="font-semibold underline">0114 2347195</a>{' '}
                  before the problem gets worse.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Sidebar -->
        <div class="lg:col-span-1">
          <div class="sticky top-24 space-y-6">
            <div class="bg-primary-50 rounded-2xl p-6 border border-primary-100">
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-4">Book a Service</h3>
              <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm mb-6">
                Full service just £80.00. Call us to arrange a convenient time.
              </p>
              <div class="space-y-3">
                <a
                  href="tel:01142347195"
                  class="flex items-center justify-center gap-2 w-full bg-primary-600 hover:bg-primary-700 text-white px-4 py-3 rounded-lg font-medium transition-colors"
                >
                  <Phone class="w-5 h-5" />
                  0114 2347195
                </a>
                <a
                  href="tel:07835204800"
                  class="flex items-center justify-center gap-2 w-full bg-white hover:bg-slate-50 text-primary-600 px-4 py-3 rounded-lg font-medium transition-colors border border-primary-200"
                >
                  <Phone class="w-5 h-5" />
                  07835 204800
                </a>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-6 border border-slate-100 shadow-sm">
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-4">Service Pricing</h3>
              <div class="space-y-3">
                <div class="flex justify-between items-center pb-3 border-b border-slate-100">
                  <span class="text-slate-600">Full service</span>
                  <span class="font-semibold text-primary-600">£80.00</span>
                </div>
                <p class="text-xs text-slate-500">
                  Price includes full inspection, cleaning, lubrication, and safety checks.
                  Parts extra if needed.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <CTA
    title="Time for a Service?"
    subtitle="Don't wait for a breakdown. Book your annual service today."
  />
</Layout>
